## Abstract Feature Documentation

For abstract/future features:

1. Add to feature-tracking.md Abstract Features section
2. Categorize by feature area (File Operations, Editor, Chat, etc.)
3. Keep description brief (1-2 sentences)
4. Create detailed plan file when ready to implement
5. Move to Planned Features table when plan is created

